{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>您的 iPhone 或 iPad 螢幕是否出現異常，例如發現壞點、觸控失靈或顯示顏色不均？在前往 Apple 直營店之前，您現在有機會透過《ScreenDoctor》這款專業級的螢幕診斷工具自行檢測顯示器。它能快速找出潛在問題，是買賣二手設備、確認維修品質，甚至是評估保固範圍的理想幫手。現在《ScreenDoctor》正限時免費，是您確保裝置顯示器運作完美的絕佳機會。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460bb-75-108.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>全面診斷螢幕缺陷掌握裝置健康</h2>\n    <p>《ScreenDoctor》提供專業級螢幕檢測，能精準偵測壞點、烙印等顯示問題，並透過觸控繪圖確認靈敏度。它更包含實用的螢幕真偽指南，協助您判斷顯示器是否為原廠，全面掌握裝置顯示健康。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-184-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-185-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-186-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-187-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-188-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1242x2688bb-189-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：ScreenDoctor</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Utilities</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T22:07:14.274237+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":341,"images":7,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}